                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9477" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1430</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1496 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“硅”途破浪，科创债引航——沪硅产业创新融资之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breaking waves with &quot;Silicon&quot;: Innovative financing path of Shanghai Silicon Industry led by Sci-Tech Bonds.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑世杰，周学媛，刘佳玲，孙小玄，赵敏，陈宇，汪丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安徽师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海硅产业集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科创债；融资困境；融资方式；技术研发</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STI Debt; Financing Dilemma; Financing Method; Technological Innovation </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">为增强企业科技创新能力，国家积极策动债券市场为科技创新提供精准且高效的服务。在此背景下，为企业科技创新提供精准资金支撑的科创债应运而生。沪硅产业集团为半导体硅片行业的佼佼者，率先响应国家政策，成功发行全国首单科创板上市公司科创债，是科技型企业发行科创债典型的代表。本案例深入剖析了沪硅产业集团发行科创债的背景、动因及其所带来的经济后果。发现，科创债不仅满足企业的融资需求，更为企业科技创新提供了强大的资金支撑。本案例为同类企业发行科创债提供了宝贵的经验证据，助力企业实现科技创新与产业升级。同时，本案例也有助于加深学生对科创债理论知识的理解，引导学生积极探索融资与创新之间的紧密联系。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> In order to enhance the technological innovation ability of enterprises, China actively instigates the bond market to provide accurate and efficient services for technological innovation. In this context, the Science and Technology Innovation debt (STI Debt), which provides accurate financial support for enterprise science and technology innovation, came into being. As a leader in China&#39;s semiconductor silicon wafer industry, Shanghai Silicon Industry Group took the lead in responding to national policies and successfully issued the first STI Debt of listed company on the STAR Market, becoming a typical representative of technology-based enterprises issuing STI Debt. This case deeply analyzes the background, motivation and economic consequences of the issuance of STI Debt by Shanghai Silicon Industry Group. It is found that STI Debt not only meet the financing needs of enterprises, but also provide strong financial support for technological innovation of enterprises. This case provides valuable empirical evidence for similar enterprises to issue STI Debt, and helps enterprises achieve technological innovation and industrial upgrading. At the same time, this case also helps to deepen students&#39; understanding of the theoretical knowledge of STI Debt, and guides students to actively explore the close relationship between financing and innovation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司理财》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科创债的概念和特点；科技创新理论；优序融资理论；资本市场融资理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-03</td>
                            </tr>
